
Common
t   Login                       P   /login      username=<>&password=<>                      {role:Admin|Student|Professor}
t   Logout                      P   /logout     foo=bar                                      {}
t   Announce                    G   /announce                                                {announce}
t   Profile                     G   /profile        {
                                                        username,
                                                        realname,
                                                        role:Admin|Student|Professor,
                                                        (if student:
                                                            department,
                                                            cls,
                                                            cls_index,
                                                            selected:id,
                                                            applied_to:id,
                                                            excluded,
                                                        )
                                                        (if professor:
                                                            department,
                                                            title,
                                                            direction,
                                                        )
                                                    }

t   Show Student                G   /student    
                                                    {student:[{
                                                        username,
                                                        realname,
                                                        cls,
                                                        cls_index,
                                                        selected:id,
                                                        applied_to:id,
                                                        excluded,
                                                    }]}
        (Filter)
t   Show Subject                G   /subject        {subject:[{
                                                        id,
                                                        name,
                                                        type1,
                                                        type2,
                                                        source,
                                                        selected_by:[{username,realname}],
                                                        applied_to:{username,realname},
                                                        professor:{realname,title,direction},
                                                    }]}
        (Filter)
t   Change PW                   P   /chpasswd   password=<>&new_password=<>                  {}

Admin
t   Import                      P   /import     professor=xxx.csv&student=xxx.csv            {}
t   Phase                       GP  /phase      password=<>                                  {phase:N}
t   Announce                    P   /announce   announce=<>                                  {}
t   Reset DB                    P   /reset      password=<>                                  {}
t   Match Student to Subject    P   /match      subject=<SubjectID>&student=<StudentID>      {}


Professor
t   Add Subject                 P   /add        name=<>&desc=<>&type1=<>&type2=<>&source=<>  {id}
t   Mod Subject                 P   /modify     id=<>&name=<>&...                            {}
t   Approve Student in Subject  P   /approve    subject=<SubjectID>&student=<StudentID>      {}

Student
t   Select Subject              P   /select     subject=<SubjectId>                          {}
t   Upload Resume               P   /resume     resume=xxx.xxx                               {}
t   Download Resume             G   /resume     student=<StudentID>                          (Raw File)
